text: Muzaffargarh District () is a district in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city of Muzaffargarh is the capital. ==Tehsils== The district Muzaffargarh is divided in to five administrative tehsils. * Alipur Tehsil * Jatoi Tehsil * Kot Addu Tehsil * Muzaffargarh * Chowk Sarwar Shaheed Tehsil Category:Districts of British India Category:Dera Ghazi Khan Division
title: Muzaffargarh District
